---
// 按系统语言分流:zh* → /zh/,其余 → /en/
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml" />
    <title>Banthropic</title>
    <script is:inline>
      var target = (navigator.language || "en").toLowerCase().indexOf("zh") === 0 ? "/zh/" : "/en/";
      location.replace(target);
    </script>
    <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="2;url=/en/" />
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: system-ui; background: #f0eee6; color: #141413; text-align: center; padding-top: 20vh">
    <p>🔨 Redirecting… / 跳转中……</p>
    <p><a href="/zh/">中文</a> · <a href="/en/">English</a></p>
  </body>
</html>
